	(text "1. All resistors 1/2 watt +/- 5% unless otherwise stated.\n2. All capacitors in MMFD (pF), 500 V.D.C.\n3. Tube unit location: G2,H2,J2,L2,M2,N2,R2,S2,T2,U2,X2,Y2,Z2.\n4. Bank 0 swaps DELAYED_BIAS and -105V in flip-flops 1 and 3."
